{{Infobox journal | title = Energy Economics | cover = Energy Economics (journal).gif | editor = B.W. Ang, U. Soytas, [[Richard Tol|R.S.J. Tol]], and [[John Weyant|J.P. Weyant]] | discipline = [[Energy economics]] | abbreviation = Energy Econ. | publisher = [[Elsevier]] | frequency = Bimonthly | history = 1979-present | openaccess = | impact = 3.199 | impact-year = 2016 | website = http://www.journals.elsevier.com/energy-economics/ | link2 = http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/journal/01409883 | link2-name = Online archive | link3 = http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/journal/10857443/3/1 | link3-name = Online archives of ''Journal of Energy Finance & Development'' | OCLC = 38907734 | LCCN = 79646092 | CODEN = EECODR | ISSN = 0140-9883 | eISSN = | ISSN2 = 1085-7443 | ISSN2label = ''Journal of Energy Finance & Development'': }} '''''Energy Economics''''' is a bimonthly [[peer-reviewed]] [[academic journal]] published by [[Elsevier]] covering the [[economic]] and [[econometric]] modelling and analysis of energy systems and issues ([[energy economics]]). The [[editors-in-chief]] are B.W. Ang ([[National University of Singapore]]), U. Soytas ([[Middle East Technical University]]), [[Richard Tol|R.S.J. Tol]] ([[University of Sussex]]), and [[John Weyant|J.P. Weyant]] ([[Stanford University]]). The ''Journal of Energy Finance & Development'' (1996-1999) was incorporated into ''Energy Economics'' in 1999.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/journal/10857443 |title=Journal of Energy Finance & Development |publisher=[[Elsevier]] |work=ScienceDirect |date= |accessdate=2014-08-26}}</ref>
